org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities

  • Packages that use org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities 
    Package Description
    org.gradoop.common.config
    Contains Configuration classes for Gradoop.
    org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities
    Contains all interfaces defining the Extended EPGMProperty Graph model.
    org.gradoop.common.model.impl.comparators
    Contains comparators for EPGM elements.
    org.gradoop.common.model.impl.pojo
    Contains a default POJO implementation of EPGM entities.
    org.gradoop.common.util
    Contains utility classes.
    org.gradoop.flink.algorithms.btgs.functions
    Flink functions related to the isolation of business transaction graphs
    org.gradoop.flink.algorithms.fsm.transactional.tle.functions
    Flink functions related to frequent subgraph mining.
    org.gradoop.flink.datagen.transactions.foodbroker.functions.process
    Functions which represent the processes of FoodBroker.
    org.gradoop.flink.datagen.transactions.foodbroker.generators
    Contains all generator classes which generate master data objects used in FoodBroker.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv.functions
    Contains functions to transform EPGM entities into CSV and vice versa.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.deprecated.json.functions
    Contains functions to transform EPGM entities into JSON and vice versa.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.graph.functions
    Contains all functions related to reading an external graph into Gradoop.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.api.functions
    Interfaces for functions that can be applied on EPGM model elements.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.comparators
    Comparators related to the EPGM data model.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.functions.epgm
    Contains map function implementations that are globally used.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.functions.graphcontainment
    Contains filter function implementations that are globally used.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.fusion.functions
    Functions required for the Nesting operation's definition
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping.functions
    Contains all user defined functions related to the graph grouping operator implementations.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common
    Contains functionality used by all pattern matching implementations.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common.functions
    Contains Flink functions that are used by all matching implementations.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.transactional.function
    Contains implementations graph pattern matching on a single input graph.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.sampling.functions
    Contains all user defined functions related graph sampling.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.tostring.tuples
    Flink tuples related to string representations
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.transformation.functions
    Contains functions required for the graph modification operator.
    org.gradoop.storage.common.api
    Contains epgm api classes for store apis
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo
    Contains storage handling classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.handler
    Contains handler classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.iterator.client
    Contains Client iterator classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.iterator.tserver
    Accumulo iterator implements
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.predicate.filter.api
    Contains element filter classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.predicate.filter.calculate
    Contains logical expressions for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.predicate.filter.impl
    Contains predicate classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.predicate.query
    Contains Query holder classes for gradoop accumulo
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase
    Contains all classes for storing EPGs in HBase.
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.api
    Contains all classes for storing EPGs.
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.handler
    Contains handler classes for gradoop hbase
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.predicate.filter.api
    Contains filter API interface related to HBase predicate definitions.

    org.gradoop.storage.utils
    HBase filter utilities
